Regulation (EC) No 3337/93 is hereby amended as follows:
1. Article 4 is amended as follows:
(a) in paragraph 1, 'ECU 105' is replaced by 'ECU 110' and 'ECU 89' is replaced by 'ECU 94';
(b) in paragraph 2, 'ECU 30' is replaced by 'ECU 36' and 'ECU 25,5' is replaced by 'ECU 31';
(c) in paragraph 3, 'ECU 23' is replaced by 'ECU 29' and 'ECU 19,5' is replaced by 'ECU 25';
2. Annex I is replaced by the Annex to this Regulation.
